{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "莫尔提斯 第1话 求知欲旺盛的莫尔提斯",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "伊莉雅的隐秘居所",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "你、好……\\n我、叫、莫尔提斯……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "就是这样！很不错嘛！\\n自我介绍已经没问题了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "自我、介绍、没问题？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "就是说你有长进了！\\n这是好事呀，莫尔提斯！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "好事。那我、很开心。\\n谢谢，伊莉雅。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "呵呵，伊莉雅和莫尔提斯\\n就像母子一样呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "让我想起了幼时和母亲\\n一起度过的那些时日。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "嗯……看到伊莉雅\\n能跟他人建立关系，\\n我的确很欣慰，可是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "因为他是异界之物，\\n果然还是不放心吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "是啊。毕竟谁也无法预测\\n超乎世间常理的生命\\n会带来什么样的影响。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "好了，莫尔提斯，\\n接下来你想学什么？\\n只要是我知道的，我都教你！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "都教？可以吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "伊莉雅，这很危险。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "危险……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "梅奈，这话什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "你也知道龙\\n厌恶异界之物吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "赋予异界之物知识\\n相当于带他进入这个世界。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "龙甚至有可能\\n会对你产生敌意……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "一味担心风险只会一事无成。\\n真到了那时候我会再想办法。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "为什么你总是这样？\\n你知道我有多担心你……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "都说你这是过度保护了！\\n我已经是大人了啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "伊莉雅……梅奈……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "你们都冷静一下……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "怎、怎么回事！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "是敌袭吗！？我去看看情况！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "啊，伊莉雅！\\n等一等！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "这声音……莫非……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "这、这是什么？\\n焦黑的破烂？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "不……这是我的实验器具。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "伊莉雅，你又在做\\n危险的实验吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "才不是！我怎么可能\\n犯这种低级错误？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "那究竟是谁……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "那个……是我……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "莫尔提斯？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "想学着、伊莉雅……\\n于是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "学我？难不成\\n你想试试炼金术吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "我想更了解、\\n伊莉雅的事……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "但是，坏了……\\n还吓到了大家……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "梅奈说的、没错……\\n我学习知识、很危险……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "莫尔提斯……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "！\\n对不起……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你好厉害呀！竟然\\n会有独立做实验的想法！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "诶？\\n你不生气吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "怎么会生气呢！\\n这是显著的成长啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "成长、是好事……\\n但是、要是我、没有学习的欲望，\\n就不会变成这样……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "莫尔提斯，你听好。\\n有一点你搞错了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "获取知识并不是坏事。\\n关键在于获取知识的人\\n拥有怎样的心。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "心……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你不是说了吗，\\n“想更了解我的事”。\\n所以你才尝试了炼金术实验。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "也就是说，你并没有恶意。\\n只是拥有纯粹的好奇心而已。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "没有人会责备你，\\n毕竟你又没干坏事。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "即便、我不是、\\n这个世界的人？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "当然啦。知识面前人人平等。\\n所有求知者都同样拥有\\n学习知识的权利。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "绝对不能因出处和种族等差异\\n而剥夺他人学习的机会。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "伊莉雅……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "身为精灵的梅奈\\n也教会了我这个人类\\n许多东西不是吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "这和我教莫尔提斯\\n有什么区别？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "话是这么说……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "而且我觉得，教给他各种知识\\n才能避免今天这种事故发生。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你了解我的话就应该知道，\\n好奇心是永无止境的吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "唉……好吧。\\n那教育莫尔提斯的任务\\n就交给你了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "谢谢你！莫尔提斯，\\n这下你就能尽情学习\\n各种知识了呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "真的可以吗？我也许、\\n又会弄坏伊莉雅的东西。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "失败乃成功之母。\\n一开始就一帆风顺的例子\\n少之又少。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "只要找到失败的原因，\\n在通往成功的道路上\\n积累经验就好。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "所以我们就一起学习吧。\\n好吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "谢谢。我想要、\\n更加了解这个世界！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}